## Account Purpose Definition

### Environment-Based Account

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Account Strategy** | Environment-based Multi-Account |
| **Environment** | {{ account_environment }} |
| **Description** | {{ account_description }} |

### Account Structure

This account represents the **{{ account_environment }}** environment. The account structure will be:

```
{{ account_environment }} Account
├── Sales databases (Data Product workflow)
├── Finance databases (Data Product workflow)
├── HR databases (Data Product workflow)
└── ... other domain databases
```

### Generated Account Name

Based on your Platform Foundation naming conventions:

{%- if account_name_prefix | upper != "NONE" %}
`{{ account_name_prefix | lower }}_{{ account_environment | lower }}`
{%- else %}
`{{ account_environment | lower }}`
{%- endif %}

